    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to share this absolute beauty with you! Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been loved and pampered since day one, and you won't find a single blemish on it\u2014it's truly pristine. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that looks and drives like a dream, this is definitely the one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
