    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This example exhibits perfect mechanical harmony, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox is precise, and the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance: the rod bearings have been replaced, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term chassis rigidity. The exterior retains its original factory depth with no signs of panel fatigue or oxidation. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters remain firm and free of wear. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist. PPIs at specialized shops are welcomed.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Original paint. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 42750.0,
