    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every inch of the original factory paint is flawless, having been preserved under a professional ceramic coating and strictly garage-kept since day one. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed at the dealership. There are no leaks, no warning lights, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained example with zero compromises. Clean title in hand, smoke-free, and ready for its next discerning owner.",
      "price": 43900.0,
