    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty! It is in truly mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for someone to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
