      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated performance. The S54 power plant features a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering seamless power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally superior, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a completely overhauled cooling system with an aluminum radiator. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers surgical engagement, complemented by a refreshed clutch assembly and a limited-slip differential with factory-spec lockup. This is a zero-fault specimen with impeccable bore-score-free history and a pristine undercarriage, catering to the most discerning BMW purist.",
